name: Churiya Muriya Shiksha Paryavaran Evum Swasthya Sewa Samiti
briefDescription: Churiya Muriya is focused on Environment issue such plantation of trees save biodiversity of the city and education and awareness on the environment issue among students. Education on Science subject is another major work churiya muriya do publish question and answer bank which is understanding based for Board students to improve their result in Board and as well as create interest in science subject main objective to generate youth team which are focused on the science issue. Work of reproductive health issue through awareness among women girls and industrial workers
